==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: malapropism
<hw>mal"a*prop*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<person>Mrs. <etsep>Malaprop</etsep></person>, a character in
<persfn>Sheridan's</persfn> drama, ⟦ldquo⟧ The Rivals,⟦rdquo⟧ who makes
amusing blunders in her use of words. See <er>Malapropos</er>.]</ety>
<def>A grotesque misuse of a word; a word so used.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>malapropos</ent>⟦br⟧
